#

Traditional Ukrainian Borshch

120 min
$10.5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Ukrainian

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodUkrainian

Description

A hearty beet soup bursting with flavor, served with a dollop of sour cream and fresh herbs.

Ingredients

  • beets: 3 medium
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • carrots: 1 large, grated
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • bay leaves: 2
  • fresh dill: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • sour cream: for serving
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
